# Penn LEAD XCP-D Derivatives

This dataset contains XCP-D derivatives for the Penn LEAD dataset (https://openneuro.org/datasets/ds007116).

The command used to XCP-D was:

```
xcp_d \
    /data/fmriprep \
    /data/xcp_d \
    participant \
    --stop-on-first-crash \
    --mode linc \
    --input-type fmriprep \
    --dummy-scans auto \
    --atlases \
        4S1056Parcels \
        4S156Parcels \
        4S256Parcels \
        4S356Parcels \
        4S456Parcels \
        4S556Parcels \
        4S656Parcels \
        4S756Parcels \
        4S856Parcels \
        4S956Parcels \
        Glasser \
        Gordon \
        HCP \
        MIDB \
        Tian
```
